11241 /// Return allocator value from expression, or return a null allocator (default
11242 /// when no allocator specified).
11243 static llvm::Value *getAllocatorVal(CodeGenFunction &CGF,
11244  const Expr *Allocator) {
11245  llvm::Value *AllocVal;
11246  if (Allocator) {
11247  AllocVal = CGF.EmitScalarExpr(Allocator);
11248  // According to the standard, the original allocator type is a enum
11249  // (integer). Convert to pointer type, if required.
11250  AllocVal = CGF.EmitScalarConversion(AllocVal, Allocator->getType(),
11251  CGF.getContext().VoidPtrTy,
11252  Allocator->getExprLoc());
11253  } else {
11254  // If no allocator specified, it defaults to the null allocator.
11255  AllocVal = llvm::Constant::getNullValue(
11256  CGF.CGM.getTypes().ConvertType(CGF.getContext().VoidPtrTy));
11257  }
11258  return AllocVal;
11259 }
11260 
11261 /// Return the alignment from an allocate directive if present.
11262 static llvm::Value *getAlignmentValue(CodeGenModule &CGM, const VarDecl *VD) {
11263  std::optional<CharUnits> AllocateAlignment = CGM.getOMPAllocateAlignment(VD);
11264 
11265  if (!AllocateAlignment)
11266  return nullptr;
11267 
11268  return llvm::ConstantInt::get(CGM.SizeTy, AllocateAlignment->getQuantity());
11269 }
11270 
11271 Address CGOpenMPRuntime::getAddressOfLocalVariable(CodeGenFunction &CGF,
11272  const VarDecl *VD) {
11273  if (!VD)
11274  return Address::invalid();
11275  Address UntiedAddr = Address::invalid();
11276  Address UntiedRealAddr = Address::invalid();
11277  auto It = FunctionToUntiedTaskStackMap.find(CGF.CurFn);
11278  if (It != FunctionToUntiedTaskStackMap.end()) {
11279  const UntiedLocalVarsAddressesMap &UntiedData =
11280  UntiedLocalVarsStack[It->second];
11281  auto I = UntiedData.find(VD);
11282  if (I != UntiedData.end()) {
11283  UntiedAddr = I->second.first;
11284  UntiedRealAddr = I->second.second;
11285  }
11286  }
11287  const VarDecl *CVD = VD->getCanonicalDecl();
11288  if (CVD->hasAttr<OMPAllocateDeclAttr>()) {
11289  // Use the default allocation.
11290  if (!isAllocatableDecl(VD))
11291  return UntiedAddr;
11292  llvm::Value *Size;
11293  CharUnits Align = CGM.getContext().getDeclAlign(CVD);
11294  if (CVD->getType()->isVariablyModifiedType()) {
11295  Size = CGF.getTypeSize(CVD->getType());
11296  // Align the size: ((size + align - 1) / align) * align
11297  Size = CGF.Builder.CreateNUWAdd(
11298  Size, CGM.getSize(Align - CharUnits::fromQuantity(1)));
11299  Size = CGF.Builder.CreateUDiv(Size, CGM.getSize(Align));
11300  Size = CGF.Builder.CreateNUWMul(Size, CGM.getSize(Align));
11301  } else {
11302  CharUnits Sz = CGM.getContext().getTypeSizeInChars(CVD->getType());
11303  Size = CGM.getSize(Sz.alignTo(Align));
11304  }
11305  llvm::Value *ThreadID = getThreadID(CGF, CVD->getBeginLoc());
11306  const auto *AA = CVD->getAttr<OMPAllocateDeclAttr>();
11307  const Expr *Allocator = AA->getAllocator();
11308  llvm::Value *AllocVal = getAllocatorVal(CGF, Allocator);
11309  llvm::Value *Alignment = getAlignmentValue(CGM, CVD);
11310  SmallVector<llvm::Value *, 4> Args;
11311  Args.push_back(ThreadID);
11312  if (Alignment)
11313  Args.push_back(Alignment);
11314  Args.push_back(Size);
11315  Args.push_back(AllocVal);
11316  llvm::omp::RuntimeFunction FnID =
11317  Alignment ? OMPRTL___kmpc_aligned_alloc : OMPRTL___kmpc_alloc;
11318  llvm::Value *Addr = CGF.EmitRuntimeCall(
11319  OMPBuilder.getOrCreateRuntimeFunction(CGM.getModule(), FnID), Args,
11320  getName({CVD->getName(), ".void.addr"}));
11321  llvm::FunctionCallee FiniRTLFn = OMPBuilder.getOrCreateRuntimeFunction(
11322  CGM.getModule(), OMPRTL___kmpc_free);
11323  QualType Ty = CGM.getContext().getPointerType(CVD->getType());
11324  Addr = CGF.Builder.CreatePointerBitCastOrAddrSpaceCast(
11325  Addr, CGF.ConvertTypeForMem(Ty), getName({CVD->getName(), ".addr"}));
11326  if (UntiedAddr.isValid())
11327  CGF.EmitStoreOfScalar(Addr, UntiedAddr, /*Volatile=*/false, Ty);
11328 
11329  // Cleanup action for allocate support.
11330  class OMPAllocateCleanupTy final : public EHScopeStack::Cleanup {
11331  llvm::FunctionCallee RTLFn;
11332  SourceLocation::UIntTy LocEncoding;
11333  Address Addr;
11334  const Expr *AllocExpr;
11335 
11336  public:
11337  OMPAllocateCleanupTy(llvm::FunctionCallee RTLFn,
11338  SourceLocation::UIntTy LocEncoding, Address Addr,
11339  const Expr *AllocExpr)
11340  : RTLFn(RTLFn), LocEncoding(LocEncoding), Addr(Addr),
11341  AllocExpr(AllocExpr) {}
11342  void Emit(CodeGenFunction &CGF, Flags /*flags*/) override {
11343  if (!CGF.HaveInsertPoint())
11344  return;
11345  llvm::Value *Args[3];
11346  Args[0] = CGF.CGM.getOpenMPRuntime().getThreadID(
11347  CGF, SourceLocation::getFromRawEncoding(LocEncoding));
11348  Args[1] = CGF.Builder.CreatePointerBitCastOrAddrSpaceCast(
11349  Addr.emitRawPointer(CGF), CGF.VoidPtrTy);
11350  llvm::Value *AllocVal = getAllocatorVal(CGF, AllocExpr);
11351  Args[2] = AllocVal;
11352  CGF.EmitRuntimeCall(RTLFn, Args);
11353  }
11354  };
11355  Address VDAddr =
11356  UntiedRealAddr.isValid()
11357  ? UntiedRealAddr
11358  : Address(Addr, CGF.ConvertTypeForMem(CVD->getType()), Align);
11359  CGF.EHStack.pushCleanup<OMPAllocateCleanupTy>(
11360  NormalAndEHCleanup, FiniRTLFn, CVD->getLocation().getRawEncoding(),
11361  VDAddr, Allocator);
11362  if (UntiedRealAddr.isValid())
11363  if (auto *Region =
11364  dyn_cast_or_null<CGOpenMPRegionInfo>(CGF.CapturedStmtInfo))
11365  Region->emitUntiedSwitch(CGF);
11366  return VDAddr;
11367  }
11368  return UntiedAddr;
11369 }
11370 
11371 bool CGOpenMPRuntime::isLocalVarInUntiedTask(CodeGenFunction &CGF,
11372  const VarDecl *VD) const {
11373  auto It = FunctionToUntiedTaskStackMap.find(CGF.CurFn);
11374  if (It == FunctionToUntiedTaskStackMap.end())
11375  return false;
11376  return UntiedLocalVarsStack[It->second].count(VD) > 0;
11377 }
11378 
11379 CGOpenMPRuntime::NontemporalDeclsRAII::NontemporalDeclsRAII(
11380  CodeGenModule &CGM, const OMPLoopDirective &S)
11381  : CGM(CGM), NeedToPush(S.hasClausesOfKind<OMPNontemporalClause>()) {
11382  assert(CGM.getLangOpts().OpenMP && "Not in OpenMP mode.");
11383  if (!NeedToPush)
11384  return;
11385  NontemporalDeclsSet &DS =
11386  CGM.getOpenMPRuntime().NontemporalDeclsStack.emplace_back();
11387  for (const auto *C : S.getClausesOfKind<OMPNontemporalClause>()) {
11388  for (const Stmt *Ref : C->private_refs()) {
11389  const auto *SimpleRefExpr = cast<Expr>(Ref)->IgnoreParenImpCasts();
11390  const ValueDecl *VD;
11391  if (const auto *DRE = dyn_cast<DeclRefExpr>(SimpleRefExpr)) {
11392  VD = DRE->getDecl();
11393  } else {
11394  const auto *ME = cast<MemberExpr>(SimpleRefExpr);
11395  assert((ME->isImplicitCXXThis() ||
11396  isa<CXXThisExpr>(ME->getBase()->IgnoreParenImpCasts())) &&
11397  "Expected member of current class.");
11398  VD = ME->getMemberDecl();
11399  }
11400  DS.insert(VD);
11401  }
11402  }
11403 }
11404 
11405 CGOpenMPRuntime::NontemporalDeclsRAII::~NontemporalDeclsRAII() {
11406  if (!NeedToPush)
11407  return;
11408  CGM.getOpenMPRuntime().NontemporalDeclsStack.pop_back();
11409 }

11414  std::pair<Address, Address>> &LocalVars)
11415  : CGM(CGF.CGM), NeedToPush(!LocalVars.empty()) {

11417  return;

11419  CGF.CurFn, CGM.getOpenMPRuntime().UntiedLocalVarsStack.size());
11420  CGM.getOpenMPRuntime().UntiedLocalVarsStack.push_back(LocalVars);
11421 }

11425  return;
11426  CGM.getOpenMPRuntime().UntiedLocalVarsStack.pop_back();

11429 bool CGOpenMPRuntime::isNontemporalDecl(const ValueDecl *VD) const {
11430  assert(CGM.getLangOpts().OpenMP && "Not in OpenMP mode.");
11431 
11432  return llvm::any_of(
11433  CGM.getOpenMPRuntime().NontemporalDeclsStack,
11434  [VD](const NontemporalDeclsSet &Set) { return Set.contains(VD); });
11435 }
11436 
11437 void CGOpenMPRuntime::LastprivateConditionalRAII::tryToDisableInnerAnalysis(
11438  const OMPExecutableDirective &S,
11439  llvm::DenseSet<CanonicalDeclPtr<const Decl>> &NeedToAddForLPCsAsDisabled)
11440  const {
11441  llvm::DenseSet<CanonicalDeclPtr<const Decl>> NeedToCheckForLPCs;
11442  // Vars in target/task regions must be excluded completely.
11443  if (isOpenMPTargetExecutionDirective(S.getDirectiveKind()) ||
11444  isOpenMPTaskingDirective(S.getDirectiveKind())) {
11445  SmallVector<OpenMPDirectiveKind, 4> CaptureRegions;
11446  getOpenMPCaptureRegions(CaptureRegions, S.getDirectiveKind());
11447  const CapturedStmt *CS = S.getCapturedStmt(CaptureRegions.front());
11448  for (const CapturedStmt::Capture &Cap : CS->captures()) {
11449  if (Cap.capturesVariable() || Cap.capturesVariableByCopy())
11450  NeedToCheckForLPCs.insert(Cap.getCapturedVar());
11451  }
11452  }
11453  // Exclude vars in private clauses.
11454  for (const auto *C : S.getClausesOfKind<OMPPrivateClause>()) {
11455  for (const Expr *Ref : C->varlists()) {
11456  if (!Ref->getType()->isScalarType())
11457  continue;
11458  const auto *DRE = dyn_cast<DeclRefExpr>(Ref->IgnoreParenImpCasts());
11459  if (!DRE)
11460  continue;
11461  NeedToCheckForLPCs.insert(DRE->getDecl());
11462  }
11463  }
11464  for (const auto *C : S.getClausesOfKind<OMPFirstprivateClause>()) {
11465  for (const Expr *Ref : C->varlists()) {
11466  if (!Ref->getType()->isScalarType())
11467  continue;
11468  const auto *DRE = dyn_cast<DeclRefExpr>(Ref->IgnoreParenImpCasts());
11469  if (!DRE)
11470  continue;
11471  NeedToCheckForLPCs.insert(DRE->getDecl());
11472  }
11473  }
11474  for (const auto *C : S.getClausesOfKind<OMPLastprivateClause>()) {
11475  for (const Expr *Ref : C->varlists()) {
11476  if (!Ref->getType()->isScalarType())
11477  continue;
11478  const auto *DRE = dyn_cast<DeclRefExpr>(Ref->IgnoreParenImpCasts());
11479  if (!DRE)
11480  continue;
11481  NeedToCheckForLPCs.insert(DRE->getDecl());
11482  }
11483  }
11484  for (const auto *C : S.getClausesOfKind<OMPReductionClause>()) {
11485  for (const Expr *Ref : C->varlists()) {
11486  if (!Ref->getType()->isScalarType())
11487  continue;
11488  const auto *DRE = dyn_cast<DeclRefExpr>(Ref->IgnoreParenImpCasts());
11489  if (!DRE)
11490  continue;
11491  NeedToCheckForLPCs.insert(DRE->getDecl());
11492  }
11493  }
11494  for (const auto *C : S.getClausesOfKind<OMPLinearClause>()) {
11495  for (const Expr *Ref : C->varlists()) {
11496  if (!Ref->getType()->isScalarType())
11497  continue;
11498  const auto *DRE = dyn_cast<DeclRefExpr>(Ref->IgnoreParenImpCasts());
11499  if (!DRE)
11500  continue;
11501  NeedToCheckForLPCs.insert(DRE->getDecl());
11502  }
11503  }
11504  for (const Decl *VD : NeedToCheckForLPCs) {
11505  for (const LastprivateConditionalData &Data :
11506  llvm::reverse(CGM.getOpenMPRuntime().LastprivateConditionalStack)) {
11507  if (Data.DeclToUniqueName.count(VD) > 0) {
11508  if (!Data.Disabled)
11509  NeedToAddForLPCsAsDisabled.insert(VD);
11510  break;
11511  }
11512  }
11513  }
11514 }
11515 
11516 CGOpenMPRuntime::LastprivateConditionalRAII::LastprivateConditionalRAII(
11517  CodeGenFunction &CGF, const OMPExecutableDirective &S, LValue IVLVal)
11518  : CGM(CGF.CGM),
11519  Action((CGM.getLangOpts().OpenMP >= 50 &&
11520  llvm::any_of(S.getClausesOfKind<OMPLastprivateClause>(),
11521  [](const OMPLastprivateClause *C) {
11522  return C->getKind() ==
11523  OMPC_LASTPRIVATE_conditional;
11524  }))
11525  ? ActionToDo::PushAsLastprivateConditional
11526  : ActionToDo::DoNotPush) {
11527  assert(CGM.getLangOpts().OpenMP && "Not in OpenMP mode.");
11528  if (CGM.getLangOpts().OpenMP < 50 || Action == ActionToDo::DoNotPush)
11529  return;
11530  assert(Action == ActionToDo::PushAsLastprivateConditional &&
11531  "Expected a push action.");
11532  LastprivateConditionalData &Data =
11533  CGM.getOpenMPRuntime().LastprivateConditionalStack.emplace_back();
11534  for (const auto *C : S.getClausesOfKind<OMPLastprivateClause>()) {
11535  if (C->getKind() != OMPC_LASTPRIVATE_conditional)
11536  continue;
11537 
11538  for (const Expr *Ref : C->varlists()) {
11539  Data.DeclToUniqueName.insert(std::make_pair(
11540  cast<DeclRefExpr>(Ref->IgnoreParenImpCasts())->getDecl(),
11541  SmallString<16>(generateUniqueName(CGM, "pl_cond", Ref))));
11542  }
11543  }
11544  Data.IVLVal = IVLVal;
11545  Data.Fn = CGF.CurFn;
11546 }
11547 
11548 CGOpenMPRuntime::LastprivateConditionalRAII::LastprivateConditionalRAII(
11549  CodeGenFunction &CGF, const OMPExecutableDirective &S)
11550  : CGM(CGF.CGM), Action(ActionToDo::DoNotPush) {
11551  assert(CGM.getLangOpts().OpenMP && "Not in OpenMP mode.");
11552  if (CGM.getLangOpts().OpenMP < 50)
11553  return;
11554  llvm::DenseSet<CanonicalDeclPtr<const Decl>> NeedToAddForLPCsAsDisabled;
11555  tryToDisableInnerAnalysis(S, NeedToAddForLPCsAsDisabled);
11556  if (!NeedToAddForLPCsAsDisabled.empty()) {
11557  Action = ActionToDo::DisableLastprivateConditional;
11558  LastprivateConditionalData &Data =
11559  CGM.getOpenMPRuntime().LastprivateConditionalStack.emplace_back();
11560  for (const Decl *VD : NeedToAddForLPCsAsDisabled)
11561  Data.DeclToUniqueName.insert(std::make_pair(VD, SmallString<16>()));
11562  Data.Fn = CGF.CurFn;
11563  Data.Disabled = true;
11564  }
11565 }
11566 
11567 CGOpenMPRuntime::LastprivateConditionalRAII
11568 CGOpenMPRuntime::LastprivateConditionalRAII::disable(
11569  CodeGenFunction &CGF, const OMPExecutableDirective &S) {
11570  return LastprivateConditionalRAII(CGF, S);
11571 }
11572 
11573 CGOpenMPRuntime::LastprivateConditionalRAII::~LastprivateConditionalRAII() {
11574  if (CGM.getLangOpts().OpenMP < 50)
11575  return;
11576  if (Action == ActionToDo::DisableLastprivateConditional) {
11577  assert(CGM.getOpenMPRuntime().LastprivateConditionalStack.back().Disabled &&
11578  "Expected list of disabled private vars.");
11579  CGM.getOpenMPRuntime().LastprivateConditionalStack.pop_back();
11580  }
11581  if (Action == ActionToDo::PushAsLastprivateConditional) {
11582  assert(
11583  !CGM.getOpenMPRuntime().LastprivateConditionalStack.back().Disabled &&
11584  "Expected list of lastprivate conditional vars.");
11585  CGM.getOpenMPRuntime().LastprivateConditionalStack.pop_back();
11586  }
11587 }
11588 
11589 Address CGOpenMPRuntime::emitLastprivateConditionalInit(CodeGenFunction &CGF,
11590  const VarDecl *VD) {
11591  ASTContext &C = CGM.getContext();
11592  auto I = LastprivateConditionalToTypes.find(CGF.CurFn);
11593  if (I == LastprivateConditionalToTypes.end())
11594  I = LastprivateConditionalToTypes.try_emplace(CGF.CurFn).first;
11595  QualType NewType;
11596  const FieldDecl *VDField;
11597  const FieldDecl *FiredField;
11598  LValue BaseLVal;
11599  auto VI = I->getSecond().find(VD);
11600  if (VI == I->getSecond().end()) {
11601  RecordDecl *RD = C.buildImplicitRecord("lasprivate.conditional");
11602  RD->startDefinition();
11603  VDField = addFieldToRecordDecl(C, RD, VD->getType().getNonReferenceType());
11604  FiredField = addFieldToRecordDecl(C, RD, C.CharTy);
11605  RD->completeDefinition();
11606  NewType = C.getRecordType(RD);
11607  Address Addr = CGF.CreateMemTemp(NewType, C.getDeclAlign(VD), VD->getName());
11608  BaseLVal = CGF.MakeAddrLValue(Addr, NewType, AlignmentSource::Decl);
11609  I->getSecond().try_emplace(VD, NewType, VDField, FiredField, BaseLVal);
11610  } else {
11611  NewType = std::get<0>(VI->getSecond());
11612  VDField = std::get<1>(VI->getSecond());
11613  FiredField = std::get<2>(VI->getSecond());
11614  BaseLVal = std::get<3>(VI->getSecond());
11615  }
11616  LValue FiredLVal =
11617  CGF.EmitLValueForField(BaseLVal, FiredField);
11618  CGF.EmitStoreOfScalar(
11619  llvm::ConstantInt::getNullValue(CGF.ConvertTypeForMem(C.CharTy)),
11620  FiredLVal);
11621  return CGF.EmitLValueForField(BaseLVal, VDField).getAddress(CGF);
11622 }
11623 
11624 namespace {
11625 /// Checks if the lastprivate conditional variable is referenced in LHS.
11626 class LastprivateConditionalRefChecker final
11627  : public ConstStmtVisitor<LastprivateConditionalRefChecker, bool> {
11628  ArrayRef<CGOpenMPRuntime::LastprivateConditionalData> LPM;
11629  const Expr *FoundE = nullptr;
11630  const Decl *FoundD = nullptr;
11631  StringRef UniqueDeclName;
11632  LValue IVLVal;
11633  llvm::Function *FoundFn = nullptr;
11634  SourceLocation Loc;
11635 
11636 public:
11637  bool VisitDeclRefExpr(const DeclRefExpr *E) {
11638  for (const CGOpenMPRuntime::LastprivateConditionalData &D :
11639  llvm::reverse(LPM)) {
11640  auto It = D.DeclToUniqueName.find(E->getDecl());
11641  if (It == D.DeclToUniqueName.end())
11642  continue;
11643  if (D.Disabled)
11644  return false;
11645  FoundE = E;
11646  FoundD = E->getDecl()->getCanonicalDecl();
11647  UniqueDeclName = It->second;
11648  IVLVal = D.IVLVal;
11649  FoundFn = D.Fn;
11650  break;
11651  }
11652  return FoundE == E;
11653  }
11654  bool VisitMemberExpr(const MemberExpr *E) {
11655  if (!CodeGenFunction::IsWrappedCXXThis(E->getBase()))
11656  return false;
11657  for (const CGOpenMPRuntime::LastprivateConditionalData &D :
11658  llvm::reverse(LPM)) {
11659  auto It = D.DeclToUniqueName.find(E->getMemberDecl());
11660  if (It == D.DeclToUniqueName.end())
11661  continue;
11662  if (D.Disabled)
11663  return false;
11664  FoundE = E;
11665  FoundD = E->getMemberDecl()->getCanonicalDecl();
11666  UniqueDeclName = It->second;
11667  IVLVal = D.IVLVal;
11668  FoundFn = D.Fn;
11669  break;
11670  }
11671  return FoundE == E;
11672  }
11673  bool VisitStmt(const Stmt *S) {
11674  for (const Stmt *Child : S->children()) {
11675  if (!Child)
11676  continue;
11677  if (const auto *E = dyn_cast<Expr>(Child))
11678  if (!E->isGLValue())
11679  continue;
11680  if (Visit(Child))
11681  return true;
11682  }
11683  return false;
11684  }
11685  explicit LastprivateConditionalRefChecker(
11686  ArrayRef<CGOpenMPRuntime::LastprivateConditionalData> LPM)
11687  : LPM(LPM) {}
11688  std::tuple<const Expr *, const Decl *, StringRef, LValue, llvm::Function *>
11689  getFoundData() const {
11690  return std::make_tuple(FoundE, FoundD, UniqueDeclName, IVLVal, FoundFn);
11691  }
11692 };
11693 } // namespace
11694 
11695 void CGOpenMPRuntime::emitLastprivateConditionalUpdate(CodeGenFunction &CGF,
11696  LValue IVLVal,
11697  StringRef UniqueDeclName,
11698  LValue LVal,
11699  SourceLocation Loc) {
11700  // Last updated loop counter for the lastprivate conditional var.
11701  // int<xx> last_iv = 0;
11702  llvm::Type *LLIVTy = CGF.ConvertTypeForMem(IVLVal.getType());
11703  llvm::Constant *LastIV = OMPBuilder.getOrCreateInternalVariable(
11704  LLIVTy, getName({UniqueDeclName, "iv"}));
11705  cast<llvm::GlobalVariable>(LastIV)->setAlignment(
11706  IVLVal.getAlignment().getAsAlign());
11707  LValue LastIVLVal =
11708  CGF.MakeNaturalAlignRawAddrLValue(LastIV, IVLVal.getType());
11709 
11710  // Last value of the lastprivate conditional.
11711  // decltype(priv_a) last_a;
11712  llvm::GlobalVariable *Last = OMPBuilder.getOrCreateInternalVariable(
11713  CGF.ConvertTypeForMem(LVal.getType()), UniqueDeclName);
11714  cast<llvm::GlobalVariable>(Last)->setAlignment(
11715  LVal.getAlignment().getAsAlign());
11716  LValue LastLVal =
11717  CGF.MakeRawAddrLValue(Last, LVal.getType(), LVal.getAlignment());
11718 
11719  // Global loop counter. Required to handle inner parallel-for regions.
11720  // iv
11721  llvm::Value *IVVal = CGF.EmitLoadOfScalar(IVLVal, Loc);
11722 
11723  // #pragma omp critical(a)
11724  // if (last_iv <= iv) {
11725  // last_iv = iv;
11726  // last_a = priv_a;
11727  // }
11728  auto &&CodeGen = [&LastIVLVal, &IVLVal, IVVal, &LVal, &LastLVal,
11729  Loc](CodeGenFunction &CGF, PrePostActionTy &Action) {
11730  Action.Enter(CGF);
11731  llvm::Value *LastIVVal = CGF.EmitLoadOfScalar(LastIVLVal, Loc);
11732  // (last_iv <= iv) ? Check if the variable is updated and store new
11733  // value in global var.
11734  llvm::Value *CmpRes;
11735  if (IVLVal.getType()->isSignedIntegerType()) {
11736  CmpRes = CGF.Builder.CreateICmpSLE(LastIVVal, IVVal);
11737  } else {
11738  assert(IVLVal.getType()->isUnsignedIntegerType() &&
11739  "Loop iteration variable must be integer.");
11740  CmpRes = CGF.Builder.CreateICmpULE(LastIVVal, IVVal);
11741  }
11742  llvm::BasicBlock *ThenBB = CGF.createBasicBlock("lp_cond_then");
11743  llvm::BasicBlock *ExitBB = CGF.createBasicBlock("lp_cond_exit");
11744  CGF.Builder.CreateCondBr(CmpRes, ThenBB, ExitBB);
11745  // {
11746  CGF.EmitBlock(ThenBB);
11747 
11748  // last_iv = iv;
11749  CGF.EmitStoreOfScalar(IVVal, LastIVLVal);
11750 
11751  // last_a = priv_a;
11752  switch (CGF.getEvaluationKind(LVal.getType())) {
11753  case TEK_Scalar: {
11754  llvm::Value *PrivVal = CGF.EmitLoadOfScalar(LVal, Loc);
11755  CGF.EmitStoreOfScalar(PrivVal, LastLVal);
11756  break;
11757  }
11758  case TEK_Complex: {
11759  CodeGenFunction::ComplexPairTy PrivVal = CGF.EmitLoadOfComplex(LVal, Loc);
11760  CGF.EmitStoreOfComplex(PrivVal, LastLVal, /*isInit=*/false);
11761  break;
11762  }
11763  case TEK_Aggregate:
11764  llvm_unreachable(
11765  "Aggregates are not supported in lastprivate conditional.");
11766  }
11767  // }
11768  CGF.EmitBranch(ExitBB);
11769  // There is no need to emit line number for unconditional branch.
11770  (void)ApplyDebugLocation::CreateEmpty(CGF);
11771  CGF.EmitBlock(ExitBB, /*IsFinished=*/true);
11772  };
11773 
11774  if (CGM.getLangOpts().OpenMPSimd) {
11775  // Do not emit as a critical region as no parallel region could be emitted.
11776  RegionCodeGenTy ThenRCG(CodeGen);
11777  ThenRCG(CGF);
11778  } else {
11779  emitCriticalRegion(CGF, UniqueDeclName, CodeGen, Loc);
11780  }
11781 }
11782 
11783 void CGOpenMPRuntime::checkAndEmitLastprivateConditional(CodeGenFunction &CGF,
11784  const Expr *LHS) {
11785  if (CGF.getLangOpts().OpenMP < 50 || LastprivateConditionalStack.empty())
11786  return;
11787  LastprivateConditionalRefChecker Checker(LastprivateConditionalStack);
11788  if (!Checker.Visit(LHS))
11789  return;
11790  const Expr *FoundE;
11791  const Decl *FoundD;
11792  StringRef UniqueDeclName;
11793  LValue IVLVal;
11794  llvm::Function *FoundFn;
11795  std::tie(FoundE, FoundD, UniqueDeclName, IVLVal, FoundFn) =
11796  Checker.getFoundData();
11797  if (FoundFn != CGF.CurFn) {
11798  // Special codegen for inner parallel regions.
11799  // ((struct.lastprivate.conditional*)&priv_a)->Fired = 1;
11800  auto It = LastprivateConditionalToTypes[FoundFn].find(FoundD);
11801  assert(It != LastprivateConditionalToTypes[FoundFn].end() &&
11802  "Lastprivate conditional is not found in outer region.");
11803  QualType StructTy = std::get<0>(It->getSecond());
11804  const FieldDecl* FiredDecl = std::get<2>(It->getSecond());
11805  LValue PrivLVal = CGF.EmitLValue(FoundE);
11806  Address StructAddr = CGF.Builder.CreatePointerBitCastOrAddrSpaceCast(
11807  PrivLVal.getAddress(CGF),
11808  CGF.ConvertTypeForMem(CGF.getContext().getPointerType(StructTy)),
11809  CGF.ConvertTypeForMem(StructTy));
11810  LValue BaseLVal =
11811  CGF.MakeAddrLValue(StructAddr, StructTy, AlignmentSource::Decl);
11812  LValue FiredLVal = CGF.EmitLValueForField(BaseLVal, FiredDecl);
11813  CGF.EmitAtomicStore(RValue::get(llvm::ConstantInt::get(
11814  CGF.ConvertTypeForMem(FiredDecl->getType()), 1)),
11815  FiredLVal, llvm::AtomicOrdering::Unordered,
11816  /*IsVolatile=*/true, /*isInit=*/false);
11817  return;
11818  }
11819 
11820  // Private address of the lastprivate conditional in the current context.
11821  // priv_a
11822  LValue LVal = CGF.EmitLValue(FoundE);
11823  emitLastprivateConditionalUpdate(CGF, IVLVal, UniqueDeclName, LVal,
11824  FoundE->getExprLoc());
11825 }
11826 
11827 void CGOpenMPRuntime::checkAndEmitSharedLastprivateConditional(
11828  CodeGenFunction &CGF, const OMPExecutableDirective &D,
11829  const llvm::DenseSet<CanonicalDeclPtr<const VarDecl>> &IgnoredDecls) {
11830  if (CGF.getLangOpts().OpenMP < 50 || LastprivateConditionalStack.empty())
11831  return;
11832  auto Range = llvm::reverse(LastprivateConditionalStack);
11833  auto It = llvm::find_if(
11834  Range, [](const LastprivateConditionalData &D) { return !D.Disabled; });
11835  if (It == Range.end() || It->Fn != CGF.CurFn)
11836  return;
11837  auto LPCI = LastprivateConditionalToTypes.find(It->Fn);
11838  assert(LPCI != LastprivateConditionalToTypes.end() &&
11839  "Lastprivates must be registered already.");
11840  SmallVector<OpenMPDirectiveKind, 4> CaptureRegions;
11841  getOpenMPCaptureRegions(CaptureRegions, D.getDirectiveKind());
11842  const CapturedStmt *CS = D.getCapturedStmt(CaptureRegions.back());
11843  for (const auto &Pair : It->DeclToUniqueName) {
11844  const auto *VD = cast<VarDecl>(Pair.first->getCanonicalDecl());
11845  if (!CS->capturesVariable(VD) || IgnoredDecls.contains(VD))
11846  continue;
11847  auto I = LPCI->getSecond().find(Pair.first);
11848  assert(I != LPCI->getSecond().end() &&
11849  "Lastprivate must be rehistered already.");
11850  // bool Cmp = priv_a.Fired != 0;
11851  LValue BaseLVal = std::get<3>(I->getSecond());
11852  LValue FiredLVal =
11853  CGF.EmitLValueForField(BaseLVal, std::get<2>(I->getSecond()));
11854  llvm::Value *Res = CGF.EmitLoadOfScalar(FiredLVal, D.getBeginLoc());
11855  llvm::Value *Cmp = CGF.Builder.CreateIsNotNull(Res);
11856  llvm::BasicBlock *ThenBB = CGF.createBasicBlock("lpc.then");
11857  llvm::BasicBlock *DoneBB = CGF.createBasicBlock("lpc.done");
11858  // if (Cmp) {
11859  CGF.Builder.CreateCondBr(Cmp, ThenBB, DoneBB);
11860  CGF.EmitBlock(ThenBB);
11861  Address Addr = CGF.GetAddrOfLocalVar(VD);
11862  LValue LVal;
11863  if (VD->getType()->isReferenceType())
11864  LVal = CGF.EmitLoadOfReferenceLValue(Addr, VD->getType(),
11865  AlignmentSource::Decl);
11866  else
11867  LVal = CGF.MakeAddrLValue(Addr, VD->getType().getNonReferenceType(),
11868  AlignmentSource::Decl);
11869  emitLastprivateConditionalUpdate(CGF, It->IVLVal, Pair.second, LVal,
11870  D.getBeginLoc());
11871  auto AL = ApplyDebugLocation::CreateArtificial(CGF);
11872  CGF.EmitBlock(DoneBB, /*IsFinal=*/true);
11873  // }
11874  }
11875 }
11876 
11877 void CGOpenMPRuntime::emitLastprivateConditionalFinalUpdate(
11878  CodeGenFunction &CGF, LValue PrivLVal, const VarDecl *VD,
11879  SourceLocation Loc) {
11880  if (CGF.getLangOpts().OpenMP < 50)
11881  return;
11882  auto It = LastprivateConditionalStack.back().DeclToUniqueName.find(VD);
11883  assert(It != LastprivateConditionalStack.back().DeclToUniqueName.end() &&
11884  "Unknown lastprivate conditional variable.");
11885  StringRef UniqueName = It->second;
11886  llvm::GlobalVariable *GV = CGM.getModule().getNamedGlobal(UniqueName);
11887  // The variable was not updated in the region - exit.
11888  if (!GV)
11889  return;
11890  LValue LPLVal = CGF.MakeRawAddrLValue(
11891  GV, PrivLVal.getType().getNonReferenceType(), PrivLVal.getAlignment());
11892  llvm::Value *Res = CGF.EmitLoadOfScalar(LPLVal, Loc);
11893  CGF.EmitStoreOfScalar(Res, PrivLVal);
11894 }
